(4045, 184, 'rows_0_col1', '<h1 class=\"h2\"><span style=\"color: #ff8700;\">Local information</span></h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-169\" src=\"http://chaletcimbria.honeydigital.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/local-information-01.jpg\" alt=\"local-information-01\" width=\"1280\" height=\"800\" />\r\n<h3>Food shopping</h3>\r\nWithin a short walk you can purchase most food provisions from local shops in Morillon Village. The local butcher offers a fantastic selection of local meats including rotisserie chicken as well as locally cured meats, local cheeses, and eggs.\r\n\r\nPast the Gondola and towards the local tourist office there is a local superette. They sell a full range of foods and other products including vegetables, salads and fruit as well as canned products, cereals, regional beers and wines. They also have a deli offering regional meats and cheeses and have a local delivery of bread in the morning.\r\n\r\nIn the main high street there is a traditional bakery selling local breads, baguettes, breakfast pastries and cakes. There is also a local pharmacy and small newsagents selling papers, maps and postcards.\r\n\r\nSupermarkets, Bakers, Butchers, Restaurants, Pharmacies\r\n\r\n[gallery link=\"none\" columns=\"2\" size=\"large\" ids=\"171,172,173,174\"]\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3>Useful Links</h3>\r\n<div class=\"col-6\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-179 size-full\" src=\"http://chaletcimbria.honeydigital.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ipad-morilon.png\" alt=\"morilon\" width=\"676\" height=\"486\" /><a class=\"primary-link\" href=\"http://www.ot-morillon.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">www.morillon.fr</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-6\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-178 size-full\" src=\"http://chaletcimbria.honeydigital.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ipad-grand-massif.png\" alt=\"winter.grand-massif.com\" width=\"676\" height=\"486\" /><a class=\"primary-link\" href=\"https://winter.grand-massif.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">winter.grand-massif.com</a></div>'),
