(4816, 212, 'rows_0_col1', '<h1 class=\"h2\"><span style=\"color: #ff8700;\">Getting here</span></h1>\r\nDescribing how to get to the Chalet... Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Maecenas vehicula nulla sed pellentesque semper. Sed pellentesque massa vel neque tincidunt, eu ultrices augue bibendum. Aliquam ac congue elit. Pellentesque quam arcu, commodo sit amet euismod nec, condimentum at augue. Nulla.\r\n\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Maecenas vehicula nulla sed pellentesque semper. Sed pellentesque massa vel neque tincidunt, eu ultrices augue bibendum. Aliquam ac congue elit. Pellentesque quam arcu, commodo sit amet euismod nec, condimentum at augue. Nulla.\r\n<div class=\"aspect-ratio\"><iframe style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d53612.493308767705!2d6.649124167111294!3d46.077926000449374!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x478c01f1f836c3a5%3A0xd271ef953a138190!2sMorillon+Grand+Massif!5e0!3m2!1sen!2suk!4v1537517759780\" width=\"100%\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Transfers &amp; Car Hire</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-189\" src=\"http://chaletcimbria.honeydigital.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/transfers.jpg\" alt=\"transfers\" width=\"1403\" height=\"936\" />\r\n<h3>Car Hire</h3>\r\nWe would generally recommend you hiring a car from the Swiss side. The rentals are in the airport and when you hire a car it will come with the local road tax labels and typically the extras like winter tyres and snow chains are included as standard. Returning is also easier to find. Swiss law doesn’t require you to carry a roadside breathalyser kit which by law you should hold. (you can buy one if you are concerned from the AA/Amazon). Hiring from the French side is cheaper but you will have these add-ons and the road tax is circa CHF40. Car Rental companies include SIXT &amp; Europecar plus Hertz\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-190\" src=\"http://chaletcimbria.honeydigital.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/car-hire.jpg\" alt=\"car-hire\" width=\"1403\" height=\"936\" />\r\n<h3>Transfers</h3>\r\nYou can transfer via coach to Tangnines and or train to Cluse and then a short tax up the mountain or a local bus service. Alternatively, there is local transfer company that services the local area and has good rates and very reliable.\r\n<div class=\"col-6\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191\" src=\"http://chaletcimbria.honeydigital.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/gomassif.png\" alt=\"gomassif\" width=\"676\" height=\"486\" /><a class=\"primary-link\" href=\"https://gomassif.com/information\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://gomassif.com/information</a></div>'),
