(5238, 222, 'rows_0_col1', '<h1 class=\"h2\"><span style=\"color: #ff8700;\">Our Chalet</span></h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-173 size-full\" src=\"http://chaletcimbria.honeydigital.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/local-information-03.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"800\" />\r\nSituated 100m from the road via a single lane track and surrounded by protected woodlands and small number of similar Chalets you have glorious views into Morillon and over to Verchaix, Samoens and towards the ColJuPlane at the top of Les Gets. The Chalet is surrounded by large lawn great for playing badminton or relaxing in the summer and the lane track allows access to the local woods and paths.\r\n\r\nSplit over 3 levels with a large Garage on the ground floor with room for storing a Car, bikes and any ski / boarding equipment. There is also a laundry area with separate washer and dryer, BBQ as well as direct access to the Chalet.\r\n\r\nOn the first floor, there is a relaxing seating area with 5 seater sofa and 2 single relaxers with a wood burner stove to take the chill away in Autumn/Spring or for deep winter evenings. The dining area has been planned to be comfortable for 8 with direct access onto an open plan well equipped kitchen. A double bedroom and bathroom are also on this floor as well as access to a first-floor terrace via glazed double doors from the dining room. The terrace is perfect for outdoor dining catching the afternoon and evening summer sun with secluded views.\r\n\r\nStairs from the lounge area give you access to the second floor and 2 comfortable twin bedrooms (zip/link beds allow these to also be doubles), both with access to their own shared terrace. A large double family room with en-suite bathroom sits at the front of the Chalet with stunning views towards the Samoens. A further family bathroom provides facilities for the twin bedrooms. Each bedroom provides storage facilities under beds and side tables as well as open hanging space. All rooms have traditional wooden shutters allowing you to snuggle up in the winter and provide protection from the summer sun and each are decorated in a simple traditional manner with modern blankets, curtains and cushions.\r\n\r\nOur fixed prices have no hidden extras and includes; Free WiFi, Linen and Towels, End of stay clean and a Welcome pack. See other services for Airport transfers, Local to the door ski hire.\r\n\r\n[smartslider3 slider=2]'),
