(5418, 226, 'rows_0_col1', '<h1 class=\"h2\"><span style=\"color: #ff8700;\">Availability</span></h1>\r\nDuring the High Season ; Winter (December to April) and Summer (July &amp; August) change overs are Friday’s unless you take a mid week break then any other day except Saturday or Sunday.\r\n\r\nDuring Low Season Spring (May and June) and Autumn (September to November) we can provide changeover flexibility for any day.\r\n\r\nThe Chalet is available on weekly rentals and long weekend breaks (exceptions over school holidays)\r\n\r\nOur price includes full use of the Chalet during the period and there are no hidden extras.\r\n\r\nThe Chalet is non smoking and any indication smoking is found to have occurred your deposit will not be returned.\r\n\r\nThe Chalet is designed for a maximum of 8 people, plus 1 baby using a travel cot. More than this number invalidates insurance and any damage incurred including fire could become your liability.\r\n[wpsbc id=\"1\" title=\"no\" legend=\"no\" legend_position=\"side\" display=\"2\" year=\"0\" month=\"0\" start=\"1\" dropdown=\"no\" jump=\"no\" history=\"1\" tooltip=\"1\" highlighttoday=\"no\" weeknumbers=\"no\" language=\"auto\" language=\"auto\"]'),
