(5552, 228, 'rows_1_col1', '<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Rates</h2>\r\n[table id=1 /]\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Enquiries</h2>\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"6\" title=\"Bookings\"]\r\n<h3>Terms and Conditions for deposits</h3>\r\nA deposit of 500euros must be paid to secure your booking, refundable one week after your holiday is completed subject to any damage or breakages. You may cancel your holiday up to 12 weeks before at no cost and the deposit returned, thereafter the deposit will not be returned but you will not need to pay the rental for the chalet. Final settlement for the chalet must be made in cleared funds 8 weeks before arrival, failure to do could result in loss of your deposit and use of the Chalet. If after payment you decide to cancel, a refund of 50% will be given if within 4 weeks of arrival and 25% if within 2 weeks. Your deposit will not be returned.'),
