(5621, 230, 'rows_0_col2_a', '<h1>For family and friends, a holiday to remember</h1>\r\nSituated 100m from the road via a single lane track and surrounded by protected woodlands and small number of similar Chalets you have glorious views into Morillon and over to Verchaix, Samoens and towards the ColJuPlane at the top of Les Gets.\r\n\r\nThe Chalet is surrounded by large lawn great for playing badminton or relaxing in the summer and the lane track allows access to the local woods and paths.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"primary-btn\" href=\"#\">More about the chalet</a>'),
