(7138, 243, 'rows_0_col1', '<h1 class=\"h2\"><span style=\"color: #ff8700;\">Availability</span></h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>During the High Season Winter (December to April) and Summer (July &amp; August) change overs are Friday’s unless you take a mid week break then any other day except Saturday or Sunday.</li>\r\n 	<li>During Low Season Spring (May and June) and Autumn (September to November) we can provide changeover flexibility for any day.</li>\r\n 	<li>The Chalet is available on weekly rentals and long weekend breaks (exceptions over school holidays)</li>\r\n 	<li>Our price includes full use of the Chalet during the period and there are no hidden extras.</li>\r\n 	<li>The Chalet is non smoking and any indication smoking is found to have occurred your deposit will not be returned.</li>\r\n 	<li>The Chalet is designed for a maximum of 8 people, plus 1 baby using a travel cot. More than this number invalidates insurance and any damage incurred including fire could become your liability.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nCheck our availability using the calendar below and submit a request.\r\n\r\n[wpsbc id=\"1\" title=\"no\" legend=\"yes\" legend_position=\"bottom\" display=\"2\" year=\"0\" month=\"0\" start=\"1\" dropdown=\"no\" jump=\"no\" history=\"1\" tooltip=\"1\" highlighttoday=\"no\" weeknumbers=\"no\" language=\"auto\" language=\"auto\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"primary-btn\" href=\"#\">Submit a request</a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAlternatively, you can book and pay now through one of our booking partners:\r\n\r\n<a class=\"primary-btn alt half\" href=\"#\">Book with [partner name]</a><a class=\"primary-btn alt half\" href=\"#\">Book with [partner name]</a>'),
